/home/nikos/go/src/go.lepak.sg/playground/slidingwindow/counter.go
func (c *Counter[T]) Observe(value T) {
	size := len(c.window)
 
	needEvict := c.lifetime >= size
	if needEvict {
		evictee := c.window[c.head]
		evicteeNextCount := c.current[evictee] - 1
		if evicteeNextCount > 0 {
			c.current[evictee] = evicteeNextCount
		} else if evicteeNextCount == 0 {
			delete(c.current, evictee)
			if c.evict != nil {
				c.evict(evictee)
			}
		} else {
			panic("evicteeCount was 0")
		}
	}
 
	c.window[c.head] = value
	c.lifetime += 1
	c.head += 1
	if c.head >= size {
		c.head = 0
	}
	c.current[value] += 1
}
